
<!--Note to self
since affectors like fade, scale will have a start and end value
there is never a need to have a fade spawn property when having a  
fade affector since the start val will be overwritten etc. 

also for this reason is a fade spawn property redundant since it can just be specified in the color if its constant.
could just have an end fade val in fade affector.
-->

